### Query focus status
GET http://{{BASE_URL}}/api/pomodoros

### Start focus for task
POST http://{{BASE_URL}}/api/pomodoro

{
    "planId": 2,
    "taskId": 3,
    "focusDuration": "PT25M",
    "focusStartTime": "2025-08-06 09:00:00"
}

### Abort focus for task
POST http://{{BASE_URL}}/api/pomodoro/1/abort

{
    "id": 1,
    "focusEndTime": "",
}

### Complete focus for task
POST http://{{BASE_URL}}/api/pomodoro/1/complete

